  "about.team.body":         { "ja": "個人プロジェクト by jasonhnd（X：@jasonhnd / GitHub：jasonhnd/jobs）", "en": "An indie project by jasonhnd (X: @jasonhnd / GitHub: jasonhnd/jobs)" },

